column5: That could of went so wrong.CRAZY

Even though I wasn't born yet I love the old James Bond movies. Some cool boat jumping in these sequences and pretty funny:  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmb3ZUAObyc  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2P9fbQik8Wg&feature=related
